dct_title_s: Colton's new sectional map of the state of Nebraska
dct_description_sm: Entered according to act of Congress in the year 1865 by G.W. & C.B. Colton ...; Prime meridians: Greenwich and Washington.; Includes inset of "Plan showing the relation of Nebraska to the adjoining states & territories" (scale [approximately 1:3,075,000]) and decorative border.
